 212:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32L4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32l4xx.c ****   *         The SystemCoreClock variable contains the core clock (HCLK), it can
 213:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32L4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32l4xx.c ****   *         be used by the user application to setup the SysTick timer or configure
 214:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32L4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32l4xx.c ****   *         other parameters.
 215:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32L4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32l4xx.c ****   *
 216:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32L4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32l4xx.c ****   * @note   Each time the core clock (HCLK) changes, this function must be called
 217:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32L4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32l4xx.c ****   *         to update SystemCoreClock variable value. Otherwise, any configuration
 218:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32L4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32l4xx.c ****   *         based on this variable will be incorrect.
 219:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32L4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32l4xx.c ****   *
 220:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32L4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32l4xx.c ****   * @note   - The system frequency computed by this function is not the real
 221:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32L4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32l4xx.c ****   *           frequency in the chip. It is calculated based on the predefined
 222:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32L4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32l4xx.c ****   *           constant and the selected clock source:
 223:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32L4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32l4xx.c ****   *
 224:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32L4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32l4xx.c ****   *           - If SYSCLK source is MSI, SystemCoreClock will contain the MSI_VALUE(*)
 225:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32L4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32l4xx.c ****   *
 226:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32L4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32l4xx.c ****   *           - If SYSCLK source is HSI, SystemCoreClock will contain the HSI_VALUE(**)
 227:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32L4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32l4xx.c ****   *
 228:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32L4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32l4xx.c ****   *           - If SYSCLK source is HSE, SystemCoreClock will contain the HSE_VALUE(***)
 229:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32L4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32l4xx.c ****   *
 230:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32L4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32l4xx.c ****   *           - If SYSCLK source is PLL, SystemCoreClock will contain the HSE_VALUE(***)
 231:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32L4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32l4xx.c ****   *             or HSI_VALUE(*) or MSI_VALUE(*) multiplied/divided by the PLL factors.
 232:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32L4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32l4xx.c ****   *
 233:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32L4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32l4xx.c ****   *         (*) MSI_VALUE is a constant defined in stm32l4xx_hal.h file (default value
 234:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32L4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32l4xx.c ****   *             4 MHz) but the real value may vary depending on the variations
 235:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/CMSIS/Device/ST/STM32L4xx/Source/Templates/system_stm32l4xx.c ****   *             in voltage and temperature.
